TY  - JOUR
TI  - Robust Tests for Heteroscedasticity Based on Regression Quantiles
AU  - Koenker, Roger
AU  - Bassett, Gilbert
AB  - [A new class of tests for heteroscedasticity in linear models based on the regression quantile statistics of Koenker and Bassett [17] is introduced. In contrast to classical methods based on least-squares residuals, the new tests are robust to departures from Gaussian hypotheses on the underlying error process of the model.]
C1  - Full publication date: Jan., 1982
DB  - JSTOR
