TY  - JOUR
TI  - Price-Quantity Strategic Market Games
AU  - Dubey, Pradeep
AB  - [A strategic model of exchange is presented in which the agents set both prices and quantities. It is shown that the strategic (Nash) equilibria are strong and coincide with the competitive (Walras) equilibria.]
